data.description: This home has ALL the space - 5 beds, over 3000sf, and the lowest price per square foot in Tartesso!  50 SOLAR panels overproduce for all your energy needs. Rich toned flooring, fresh paint throughout, and a beautiful living/dining room - plus a den perfect for an office.  Open concept kitchen with recessed lighting, a large peninsula and pantry for all of your storage.  A huge great room is attached large enough for everything on your wish list.  All bedrooms are upstairs, including a double-door owner's suite with a huge private balcony for those quiet mornings.  Massive restroom with a separate tub and shower, and TWO full-sized walk-in closets.  Easy access to the 10, great schools, parks, and shopping spots.
